title: Business rates valuation account: sign in or set up

heading_context: Business rates valuation account: sign in or set up
chunks.html_content:
Use your business rates valuation account to:

  • report changes that might affect your property’s rateable value to the Valuation Office Agency (VOA)
  • challenge your property’s rateable value
  • appoint an agent to deal with the VOA for you

This account is for properties in England and Wales.
